==MacGyver pronounced: Mac-Guy-ver==

===Verb===

{{en-infl-irreg|MacGyver|MacGyvers|MacGyvering|MacGyvered|MacGyvered}}

From a once popular American television program with the same name.

#. To assemble, or cause to be repaired or completed, an object or project from items not normally used for that purpose.  Especially: if the items are used in ways significantly different than their intended use.
#. To hastily complete a project or repair in a manner and with items not normally intended for that purpose.

:Example: Our car broke down and we didn't have any tools but Jim '''MacGyvered''' it with some toenail clippers and we were able to limp to the service station.